Interfaces `$ZodIssueTooSmall` and `$ZodIssueTooBig` type `minimum` and `maximum` properties respectively as `number | bigint`:

https://github.com/colinhacks/zod/blob/3b946107b6c94b2ac8ff9fb451160c34dc4dd794/packages/zod/src/v4/core/errors.ts#L26-L44

This misses the `Date` variant that occurs at runtime when validating `z.date().min()` or `z.date().max()`:

https://github.com/colinhacks/zod/blob/3b946107b6c94b2ac8ff9fb451160c34dc4dd794/packages/zod/src/v4/core/checks.ts#L64-L68

