/// CR 613.4c: Layer 7c — Effects that modify P/T (+N/+N).
ModifyPT,
/// CR 613.4d: Layer 7d — Effects that switch P/T.
SwitchPT,
/// CR 613.4c: Layer 7e — +1/+1 and -1/-1 counters modifying P/T (applied after other 7c effects).
CounterPT,
```

The comment cites `CR 613.4c` for `CounterPT` (correct), but then calls it "Layer 7e" and physically orders the variant after `SwitchPT` (7d) — there is no layer 7e in the CR, and counters are part of 7c, not a post-7d step.

