pub fn apnap_order(state: &GameState) -> Vec<PlayerId> { ... }
```

It is used for player-choice sequencing in ~10 other modules (`casting.rs`, `combat.rs`, `effects/vote.rs`, `effects/explore.rs`, `effects/choose_and_sacrifice_rest.rs`, `effects/separate_piles.rs`, `engine.rs`, …) — but the trigger sort sites in `triggers.rs` do not use it.

