When a player resolves a "choose one or more"/villainous-choice effect, `crate::game::effects::choose_one_of::resolve_branch` binds the chosen branch's *scoped player* to the **chooser** and then resolves the branch:

```rust
// crates/engine/src/game/effects/choose_one_of.rs:135-145
let mut resolved = build_resolved_from_def(branch, source_id, controller);
resolved.context = context;
resolved.targets = parent_targets;
resolved.set_scoped_player_recursive(player);   // player = the CHOOSER
if !resolved.targets.iter().any(|t| matches!(t, TargetRef::Player(pid) if *pid == player)) {
    resolved.targets.push(TargetRef::Player(player));
