### Describe the bug

You have a function that awaits a `setTimeout` and then throws an error.

Test this function using fake timers. Call the function and remember the promise. Advanced the time to resolve the promise. You can then successfully assert that the promise throws an error.

Once the test has completed, vitest reports an unhandled error.

